# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Djinni.co Scraper — Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your values.
# .env is gitignored and will never be committed.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Paste the full Cookie header from a djinni.co request here.
#
# How to get it (includes the required HttpOnly sessionid):
#   1. Open https://djinni.co in Chrome/Firefox (must be logged in)
#   2. Open DevTools → Network tab (F12 → Network)
#   3. Reload the page
#   4. Click any djinni.co request (e.g. the main document)
#   5. In "Request Headers" find the "cookie:" row
#   6. Right-click → Copy value  (or select all and copy)
#   7. Paste it below between the quotes
#
# The value should include sessionid=... — that is the key cookie.
# Without sessionid your IP will be blocked after a few requests.
#
DJINNI_COOKIES="csrftoken=YOUR_CSRF_TOKEN; sessionid=YOUR_SESSION_ID"
